$value['share_desc']
<p><b>Note</b>: As mentioned in the Registration Guidelines, you need to do the following steps:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Follow our Instagram and TikTok accounts: 
        <a href="https://www.instagram.com/youthbreaktheboundaries/">Youth Break the Boundaries Instagram</a>,
        <a href="https://www.instagram.com/koreayouthsummit/">Korea Youth Summit Instagram</a>,
        <a href="https://www.tiktok.com/@youthbreaktheboundaries">Youth Break the Boundaries TikTok</a>, 
        <a href="https://www.tiktok.com/@koreayouthsummit">Korea Youth Summit TikTok</a>
    </li>
    <li>Join our Telegram channels: 
        <a href="https://t.me/youthbreaktheboundaries">Youth Break the Boundaries Telegram channel</a>, 
        <a href="https://t.me/koreayouthsummit">Korea Youth Summit Telegram channel</a>
    </li>
    <li>Subscribe to the <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@ybbfoundation">YBB YouTube channel</a></li>
    <li>Tag 5 of your friends and @youthbreaktheboundaries @koreayouthsummit on your posted twibbon on Instagram or any other social media platform.</li>
    <li>Share the program information for the Korea Youth Summit (<a href="https://bit.ly/POSTERKYS2025">Korea Youth Summit Poster & Caption</a>) with 3 WhatsApp groups or any other social media groups.</li>
</ul>
<p>Take a screenshot of each action mentioned above and upload them to your storage drive. Then, copy the link and paste it into the input forms provided above. Ensure that the folder is accessible to the public and not private.</p>

confirmation_desc => UTF-8 string (1614) "<h1 style="color: #333;">Korea Youth Summit 2025</h1> <p style="margin-botto...
$value['confirmation_desc']
<h1 style="color: #333;">Korea Youth Summit 2025</h1>
<p style="margin-bottom: 10px; color: #555;">The Korea Youth Summit offers both <strong style="color: #1389FD;">Fully Funded</strong> and <strong style="color: #1389FD;">Self-Funded</strong> opportunities. To qualify for <strong style="color: #1389FD;">Full Funding</strong>, delegates must complete all registration steps and meet the payment deadline. If not selected for Full Funding, delegates can still participate through the self-funded scheme.</p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 10px; color: #555;">The comprehensive expenses outlined in the Korea Youth Summit payment cover accommodation throughout the program (<strong style="color: #1389FD;">June 30 - July 03, 2025</strong>), including airport transfers on the first day (<strong style="color: #1389FD;">June 30, 2025</strong>, from the airport to the hotel) and the last day of the program (<strong style="color: #1389FD;">July 03, 2025</strong>, from the hotel to the airport). Please note that all fully funded and self-funded payments do not include flight tickets or visa expenses. Fully funded spots will be awarded based on the quality of applicants.</p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 20px; color: #555;">Let’s join hands and collaborate at the Korea Youth Summit 2025. Your involvement is <strong style="color: #1389FD;">essential</strong> for a powerful and <strong style="color: #1389FD;">meaningful</strong> experience.</p>
<p style="font-style: italic; text-align: center; color: #555;">I am <strong>ready</strong> to join the Korea Youth Summit 2025 in <strong>Seoul, South Korea</strong>.</p>
